{"tid":982402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"提高長者綜援門檻爭議　建制派接中聯辦溫馨提示 「鬧少句」","createTime":"2019-01-15T06:00:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-16T05:37:09.000Z","uid":39464,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ad331ec467a685b8739e644925a1a07d8c792361","tid":982402,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T06:00:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190115/s00001/16d3c45c9377c2b9ee26979337e84f0e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190115%2Fs00001%2F16d3c45c9377c2b9ee26979337e84f0e.jpg&h=f85393dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府下月起將申領長者綜援年齡由60歲上調至65歲，引來泛民及建制派批評。不過《明報》「李先知」專欄指，來自不同黨派的建制議員證實，「中聯辦近日已溫馨提示大家『鬧少句』」。<br />\n<br />\n今日刊出的「李先知」專欄表示，來自不同黨派的建制議員證實，面對建制派連日來向特首林鄭月娥發炮，中聯辦近日已溫馨提示「鬧少句」。「李先知」引述建制人士分析，中聯辦或擔心政府與建制派「相嗌唔好口」，令事件惡化；另一建制人士則說，面對三隧分流、調高長者綜援申領年齡兩項直接影響民生的政策，建制派大條道理不「收口」，否則對年底區議會選舉有更大影響。<br />\n<br />\n惟「李先知」提到，雖然泛民、建制異口同聲要求擱置新政策，但面對泛民不斷建議聯手逼政府收回成命，「建制派有很大的保留和憂慮」，並引述建制中人表示，有關做法對建制派而言是開了先例，變相是與反對派共同脅迫政府，所以建制派不會與民主派「合流」。<br />\n<br />\n「李先知」另引述了政府中人回應，詳情請瀏覽《明報》今日（1月15日）刊出的李先知專欄。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190115/s00001/1547514838132/【李先知專欄】提高長者綜援門檻爭議-建制派接中聯辦溫馨提示\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190115%2Fs00001%2F1547514838132%2F%E3%80%90%E6%9D%8E%E5%85%88%E7%9F%A5%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84%E3%80%91%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98%E9%95%B7%E8%80%85%E7%B6%9C%E6%8F%B4%E9%96%80%E6%AA%BB%E7%88%AD%E8%AD%B0-%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6%E6%B4%BE%E6%8E%A5%E4%B8%AD%E8%81%AF%E8%BE%A6%E6%BA%AB%E9%A6%A8%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA&d=IaM7PEbqaTm0p1rdo6owMUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=20ee1076\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190115%2Fs00001%2F1547514838132%2F%E3%80%90%E6%9D%8E%E5%85%88%E7%9F%A5%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84%E3%80%91%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98%E9%95%B7%E8%80%85%E7%B6%9C%E6%8F%B4%E9%96%80%E6%AA%BB%E7%88%AD%E8%AD%B0-%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6%E6%B4%BE%E6%8E%A5%E4%B8%AD%E8%81%AF%E8%BE%A6%E6%BA%AB%E9%A6%A8%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA&h=205ae630\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190115/s00001/1547514838132/【李先知專欄】提高長者綜援門檻爭議-建制派接中聯辦溫馨提示</a>"},{"pid":"376fbf7bd3d51741afe7ea036f2cfacd0225145d","tid":982402,"uid":60074,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T06:02:28.000Z","msg":"橡皮圖章學人吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f10ee31f673a9cbf8af403dea6efb74fc35912e7","tid":982402,"uid":173598,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T06:21:19.000Z","msg":"泛民可以 all in 建制票倉向廢老宣揚一下建制派點成功爭取收緊長者綜援門檻喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39b1799f3226ad38ddfd35359361a1b61b9cc2a5","tid":982402,"uid":70786,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T06:23:29.000Z","msg":"Chok一Chok條狗帶d建制賤畜即刻收聲唔吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eab3880af199a4119e7ecfee02b482cf9114f582","tid":982402,"uid":41477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T06:24:20.000Z","msg":"贊成派議員點會反對"},{"pid":"a632b01e54c12b7e74a164d61cb3b60338153d71","tid":982402,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T06:25:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d21037a8b9be61ed561089865f9dfca43ae07df","tid":982402,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T06:26:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"805b604e8c05cfeb156c900124407a49b3f9fb86","tid":982402,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":